-- Gaspar Says Portugal Must Stick to Bailout Program, Diario Says
-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 2012-03-20T08:12:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-20/gaspar-says-portugal-must-stick-to-bailout-program-diario-says.html
Portugal  must stick to its bailout
program as the country’s success hinges on increased
credibility, Diario Economico said, citing an interview with
Finance Minister Vitor Gaspar.  Portugal’s adjustment will be faster and more successful
than expected, Gaspar was cited by Diario Economico as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
